iday's final.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Saunderswon a silver medal at the Tokyo Gamesand, at the ceremony, crossed their arms and formed an \\\"X\\\" with their wrists.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Saundersexplained the \\\"X\\\" stood for\\\"the intersection of where all people who are oppressed meet.\\\"\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old from Charleston, South Carolina, competed at Southern Illinois before transferring to Ole Miss.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siege_of_Charleston\", \"score\": 0.529829624800792, \"rank\": 0.7730846762938121, \"text\": \"Charleston, South Carolina\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siege_of_Charleston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siege_of_Charleston\"}, {\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siege_of_Charleston\", \"score\": 0.529829624800792, \"rank\": 0.7730846762938121, \"text\": \"Charleston, South Carolina\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siege_of_Charleston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Siege_of_Charleston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They won NCAA shot put titles at both schools, in 2015 and 2016.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9655452413653722, \"rank\": 0.03568257011079469, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}]}]}"